com.camerontec.catalys.util.marketdata

Class FixMarketDataInstrument

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.util.marketdata.StandardInstrument
      • com.camerontec.catalys.util.marketdata.FixMarketDataInstrument
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDepthUpdate, IDetailUpdate, IFixMarketDataInstrument, IInstrument, ISecurityDefinitionUpdate, ITopOfBookUpdate, Comparable<IInstrument>

    public class FixMarketDataInstrument
extends StandardInstrument
implements IFixMarketDataInstrument
    Instrument class specific to the Market Data Server Daisy Chain, in which the source of Market Data is also FIX. This class stores additional information that is needed to process updates from the FIX source side of the server.
